131	\subsection{The short exact sequence of sheaves}
132	
133	The connecting homomorphism of the Mayer--Vietoris sequence is built from a short exact sequence of sheaves of $k$-modules obtained by sheafifying the Yoneda embedding composed with the free-$k$-module functor.
134	
135	\begin{definition}\leanok
136	[Free-$k$-module functor is left adjoint]
137	  \label{def:Scheme_ModuleCat_free_isLeftAdjoint}
138	  \lean{AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.ModuleCat_free_isLeftAdjoint}
